Here is my map surf_origine she is in a dark surround then livens with multiple colored lights, it is large enough.
It is composed of 3 main ramps (noob, normal, pro), a jail which has 3 floors and at level 2 and 3 can activate the opening of a water valve, which floods the jail (fun: p ), there are 3 levels and lots of top secret that Resident Evil ... Good Luck! and yet another.
For weapons, you just go to spawn, turn the arrow and go, you appear before a surf ramp and you should go at the highest level to have the best weapon, reached the top press the button of 'weapon and hop!
The gun shop: (? ..) It's a prefabs I downloaded, shoot the weapon you want and the seller will sell you ^^.
